### GET all films
GET http://localhost:3000/api/films

### GET favorite films
GET http://localhost:3000/api/films?filter=filter-favorite

### GET best rated films
GET http://localhost:3000/api/films?filter=filter-best

### GET unseen films
GET http://localhost:3000/api/films?filter=filter-unseen

### GET films seen in the last month
GET http://localhost:3000/api/films?filter=filter-lastmonth

### GET a specific film by ID (e.g., ID 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/films/1

### GET a film that does not exist (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/films/999

### POST - Add a new film
# La risposta dovrebbe essere un 201 Created con l'ID del nuovo film.
POST http://localhost:3000/api/films
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Nuovo Film di Prova",
    "isFavorite": true,
    "rating": 4,
    "watchDate": "2024-05-20",
    "userId": 1
}

### PUT - Update an entire film (e.g., film with ID 2)
# Questa rotta ora aggiorna l'intero film.
# Puoi passare solo i campi che vuoi cambiare.
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/films/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Pulp Fiction (Updated)",
    "isFavorite": false,
    "rating": 5,
    "watchDate": "2024-01-01",
    "userId": 1
}


### PUT - Update only the rating of a film (e.g., film with ID 3)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/films/7/rating
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "rating": 1
}


### PUT - Update a film that does not exist (should return 404)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/films/999/rating
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "rating": 5
}

### DELETE a film (e.g., film with ID 6)
# NOTA: Questo cancellerà permanentemente il film dal database.
# La risposta dovrebbe essere un 204 No Content (nessun corpo).
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/films/6

### DELETE a film that does not exist (should return 404)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/films/999
